title: MFLEX Invites The Public To Join Its 2015 Third Quarter Financial Results Conference Call And Webcast On November 5, 2015
text: MFLEX Invites The Public To Join Its 2015 Third Quarter Financial Results Conference Call And Webcast On November 5, 2015   Published on 2015-10-22 14:44:59 MFLEX Invites The Public To Join Its 2015 Third Quarter Financial Results... -- Irvine, Calif.  <-   Irvine, Calif.   Multi-Fineline Electronix, Inc. (NASDAQ: MFLX ), a leading global provider of high-quality, technologically advanced flexible printed circuits and assemblies, announced today that it will host a conference call and webcast to review its 2015 third quarter financial results on November 5, 2015 , at 5:30 p.m. Eastern time ( 2:30 p.m. Pacific time ). The Company's financial results are expected to be released at 4:30 p.m. Eastern time ( 1:30 p.m. Pacific time ) the same day and will be posted on the Company's website at www.mflex.com . DETAILS MFLEX's 2015 third quarter financial results conference call and webcast DATE: Thursday, November 5, 2015 TIME: 5:30 p.m. Eastern time ( 2:30 p.m. Pacific time ) HOW A live webcast of the call will be available on the Company's website www.mflex.com . Alternatively, the telephone dial-in number is 1-877-876-9177 for callers in North America and 1-785-424-1666 for international callers. The Conference ID is 397445. REPLAYS The webcast will be archived on the Company's website for at least 60 days following the call. An audio replay of the conference call will be available for seven days beginning at 8:30 p.m. Eastern time ( 5:30 p.m. Pacific time ) on November 5, 2015 . The audio replay dial-in number is 1-888-203-1112 for North America and 1-719-457-0820 for international callers. The replay pass code is 397445. About MFLEX MFLEX ( www.mflex.com ) is a global provider of high-quality, technologically advanced flexible printed circuits and assemblies to the electronics industry. The Company is one of a limited number of manufacturers that provides a seamless, integrated end-to-end flexible printed circuit solution for customers, ranging from design and application engineering, prototyping and high-volume manufacturing to turnkey component assembly and testing. The Company targets its solutions within the electronics market and, in particular, focuses on applications where flexible printed circuits are the enabling technology in achieving a desired size, shape, weight or functionality of an electronic device. Current applications for the Company's products include smartphones, tablets, computer/data storage, portable bar code scanners, personal computers, wearables and other consumer electronic devices. MFLEX's common stock is quoted on the Nasdaq Global Select Market under the symbol MFLX.
